<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>GOD WILL TAK CARE OF YOU</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Pathien in hun veng ina, laukiu in,
 Nisa leh liepa hun Vengpa ahi;
 Nunnem in Amah ate A veng hi,
 Ngawna vakvai din hun nusie puo'n a.

[V2]
 Pathien in hun veng ina tawp chanin,
 Pa, Tanpa leh Guol pha pen chuh ahi;
 Isun na sap chengin hun dawng ina,
 Aman hun veng ina Amah gingin.

[V3]
 2. Pathien in hun veng ina nitum in,
 Na kalsuon vengin, hun pui zel ina;
 Na Belampu, nang hun chingpa ahi,
 A chate tui luonna munah A pui.

[V4]
 3. Pathien in hun veng ina, damsung in,
 Mi piek theihloh vangsakna hun pie'n a;
 Phat tawp chanin Aman hun veng ina,
 A tawp leh A gamah hun pui ina.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>434</hymn_number>
</song>